text: Eunidia spilotoides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939.BioLib.cz - Eunidia spilotoides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Eunidia spilotoides snizekiana Téocchi, Jiroux & Sudre, 2004 * Eunidia spilotoides spilotoides Breuning, 1939 ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1939
